                     <hot>quotient of continuous maps</hot>
                     <crossref>
                        <theorem.ref theoremID="Thm_QuotientContinuous"/>
                        <info>
                           <para>
                              <para.body>Look up this result.</para.body>
                           </para>
                        </info>
                     </crossref>
                  </subordinate>. So <math>
                     <latex>p/q</latex>
                  </math> is continuous on <math>
                     <latex>(\StDffrnc{\RNr}{Z})</latex>
